# Shared Package (`@navo/shared`)

## Files

- `shared/src/index.ts` — Shared TypeScript types (`ServerEvent`, message types, user types)
- `shared/src/i18n.ts` — i18n key definitions used by server and web

## Conventions

- Must build first: `npm -w @navo/shared run build` before server/web build
- Imported as source via tsconfig paths in dev; built dist in production
- Changes here affect both server and web — update both consumers

